    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This unit showcases exceptional mechanical health, with the dual-VANOS system operating flawlessly and rod bearings recently serviced to factory tolerances. Power is delivered through a precise six-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains rigid with a reinforced rear subframe and original suspension geometry. Finished in showroom-quality paint with a pristine undercarriage, this vehicle represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. Documentation confirms rigorous adherence to Inspection II service intervals.",
      "price": 46500.0,
